high_descs: Turn around, walk to the counter across the room, hang a right and turn left to face the white stove.
Pick up the knife from the back of the counter top to the right of the stove.
Slice the apple on the right side of the counter.
Set the knife down to the left of the apple on the counter.
Pick up a slice of apple from the counter top.
Turn left and walk to the white stove on your right.
Place the apple inside the pan in the upper left corner of the stove top.
Pick up the pan with the apple from the stove top.
Turn left, hang a left at the end of the counter and walk to the fridge.
Open the doors, place the pan with the apple into the fridge on the shelf above the round silver bowl and close the doors.
anns.task_desc: Chill an apple slice in a pan in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the oven
Grab the knife that is on the right of the stove
Cut the apple on the counter into three slices
Put the knife on the counter
Grab one of the apple slices
Turn left and stop at the oven
Put the apple in the bowl in the top right stove
Grab the bowl with the apple in it
Turn to the right and head to the fridge
Put the bowl in the second rack of the right side of the fridge
anns.task_desc: Putting a bowl with an apple slice in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around, go towards the oven, turn right, go to towards the wall, turn left to face the counter to the right of the oven.
Take the large knife from the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into pieces.
Put the knife on the counter to the left of the apple.
Take a piece of apple from the counter.
Go to the left and face the oven.
Put the apple piece in the pot on the left side of the stove top.
Take the pot from the stove top.
Turn around, go forward to the fridge.
Put the pot on the middle shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with an apple in it in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the right counter of the oven
Grab the knife that is to the right of the oven
Cut the apple on the counter into three slices
Put the knife on the counter
Grab one of the apple slices
Turn left and stop at the oven
Put the apple in the bowl in the top left stove
Grab the bowl from the top left stove
Turn around and go to the fridge
Put the bowl in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Putting a bowl with a apple slice in it in the fridge

high_descs: Moved to the right Side of the oven
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle on top of the counter
Slice the apple on top of the right side of the counter
Placed the knife on top of the counter by apple
Pick up a slice of apple on top of the counter
Move to face the left side of the stovetop
Place the apple in the pan on the back left burner
Pick up the pan with the apple in it
Carry the pan to the fridge
Place the pan on the second shelf from the top, close the fridge
anns.task_desc: Slice and apple to place in a pen in the fridge

high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the white stove
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle on top of the counter
Cut the apple sitting on the counter
Place the knife on the counter
Pick up a slice of the cut apple on top of the counter
Carry the apple to the stove top
Place the apple inside of the stainless bin
Pick up the stainless bin with the apple inside of it
Carry the stainless bin with the apple to the fridge
Place the stainless bin with the apple inside of the fridge, close the door
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple slice to store in fridge
